001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007/**
008 * NOTE, replaced by {@link DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog} in recent firmware
009 */
010@HistoryLogProps(
011    opCode = 211,
012    displayName = "CGM GX Data Sample",
013    usedByTidepool = true
014)
015public class CgmDataGxHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
016    
017    private int status;
018    private int type;
019    private int rate;
020    private int rssi;
021    private int value;
022    private long timestamp;
023    private long transmitterTimestamp;
024    
025    public CgmDataGxHistoryLog() {}
026    public CgmDataGxHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int status, int type, int rate, int rssi, int value, long timestamp, long transmitterTimestamp) {
027        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
028        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, status, type, rate, rssi, value, timestamp, transmitterTimestamp);
029        this.status = status;
030        this.type = type;
031        this.rate = rate;
032        this.rssi = rssi;
033        this.value = value;
034        this.timestamp = timestamp;
035        this.transmitterTimestamp = transmitterTimestamp;
036        
037    }
038
039    public CgmDataGxHistoryLog(int status, int type, int rate, int rssi, int value, long timestamp, long transmitterTimestamp) {
040        this(0, 0, status, type, rate, rssi, value, timestamp, transmitterTimestamp);
041    }
042
043    public int typeId() {
044        return 211;
045    }
046
047    /**
048     * <table border="1">
049     * <caption>Parsed fields for CgmDataGxHistoryLog:</caption>
050     * <tr><td><code>status</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
051     * <tr><td><code>type</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
052     * <tr><td><code>rate</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
053     * <tr><td><code>rssi</code></td><td><code>raw[15]</code></td></tr>
054     * <tr><td><code>value</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
055     * <tr><td><code>timestamp</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
056     * <tr><td><code>transmitterTimestamp</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
057     * </table>
058     */
059    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
060        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
061        this.cargo = raw;
062        parseBase(raw);
063        this.status = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
064        this.type = raw[12];
065        this.rate = raw[13];
066        this.rssi = raw[15];
067        this.value = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
068        this.timestamp = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
069        this.transmitterTimestamp = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 22);
070        
071    }
072
073    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int status, int type, int rate, int rssi, int value, long timestamp, long transmitterTimestamp) {
074        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
075            new byte[]{-45, 0}, // (byte) 211
076            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
077            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
078            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(status), 
079            new byte[]{ (byte) type }, 
080            new byte[]{ (byte) rate }, 
081            new byte[]{ (byte) rssi }, 
082            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(value), 
083            Bytes.toUint32(timestamp), 
084            Bytes.toUint32(transmitterTimestamp)));
085    }
086
087    public int getStatus() {
088        return status;
089    }
090    public int getType() {
091        return type;
092    }
093    public int getRate() {
094        return rate;
095    }
096    public int getRssi() {
097        return rssi;
098    }
099    public int getValue() {
100        return value;
101    }
102    public long getTimestamp() {
103        return timestamp;
104    }
105    public long getTransmitterTimestamp() {
106        return transmitterTimestamp;
107    }
108    
109}
